ists]]\n[[Category:English comedy writers]]\n[[Category:English film directors]]\n[[Category:English former Christians]]\n[[Category:English humanists]]\n[[Category:English humorists]]\n[[Category:English male comedians]]\n[[Category:English male film actors]]\n[[Category:English male screenwriters]]\n[[Category:English male television actors]]\n[[Category:English male voice actors]]\n[[Category:English new wave musicians]]\n[[Category:English people of Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:English people of French descent]]\n[[Category:English people of French-Canadian descent]]\n[[Category:English podcasters]]\n[[Category:British men podcasters]]\n[[Category:English radio DJs]]\n[[Category:English satirists]]\n[[Category:English screenwriters]]\n[[Category:English social commentators]]\n[[Category:English stand-up comedians]]\n[[Category:English television directors]]\n[[Category:English television producers]]\n[[Category:English television writers]]\n[[Category:LGBT rights activists from the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Berkshire]]\n[[Category:Male new wave singers]]\n[[Category:Male television writers]]\n[[Category:Outstanding Performance by a Lead Actor in a Comedy Series Primetime Emmy Award winners]]\n[[Category:People from Reading, Berkshire]]\n[[Category:Primetime Emmy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Secular humanists]]\n[[Category:Showrunners]]\n[[Category:Social critics]]\n[[Category:Writers Guild of America Award winners]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|English comedian, actor, director, and writer}}\n{{Use British English|date=January 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Ricky Gervais\n| image              = Ricky Gervais 2010.jpg\n| image_size         = \n| caption            = Gervais in 2010\n| alt                =\n| birth_name         = Ricky Dene Gervais\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1961|6|25}}\n| birth_place        = [[Reading, Berkshire]], England\n| alma_mater 