st TV Comedy Actor]] || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award]] || [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Miniseries, Movie or a Dramatic Special|Outstanding Writing for a Miniseries, Movie or a Dramatic Special]] || ''[[The Office Christmas specials]]'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[TCA Awards]] || [[TCA Award for Outstanding Achievement in Movies, Miniseries and Specials]] || rowspan=3|''The Office'' || {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=14|2006 || rowspan=2|[[Writers Guild of America Award]] || [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Comedy Series|Television: Comedy Series]] || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: New Series|Television: New Series]] || {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[British Academy Television Awards]] || [[British Academy Television Award for Best Situation Comedy|Best Situation Comedy]] || rowspan=7|''Extras'' || {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Writer || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Banff World Television Festival]] ||Best Comedy Program || {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[British Comedy Awards]] || [[British Comedy Awards#2006|Best TV Comedy]] || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[British Comedy Awards#2006|Best TV Comedy Actor]] || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Broadcasting Press Guild Awards]] || Best Comedy/Entertainment || {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Rose d'Or|Rose d'Or Light Entertainment Festival]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4809312.stm |title=Entertainment, Rose d'Or honour for TV's Gervais |work=BBC News |date=15 March 2006 |accessdate=21 November 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060423095932/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4809312.stm |archive-date=23 April 2006 |url-status=live }}</ref> || [[Rose d'Or#2006|Honorary Rose for Exceptional Contribution to the Global Entertainment Business]] || {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[Primetime Emmy Award]] || [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Comedy Series|Outstanding Comedy Series]] || ''The Office'' || {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Comedy Series|O